description: Go wanted to catch as many Pokémon as he could and one day while in a forest in the Kanto region, he caught every Bug type Pokémon native to Kanto. It was the first Kanto Bug Pokémon Go caught and he just threw the Poké Ball at it to capture it. Caterpie resides at a habitat at the Sakuragi Institute in Vermilion City.
name: Caterpie (Gou)
